com.amplifyframework.core.model.temporal

Class Temporal.DateTime

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.core.model.temporal.Temporal.DateTime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Temporal.DateTime>
    Enclosing class:
    Temporal

    public static final class Temporal.DateTime
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Temporal.DateTime>
    Represents a valid extended ISO-8601 DateTime string. The time zone offset is compulsory.

    YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ss.sssZ (ISO_OFFSET_DATE_TIME)

    https://docs.aws.amazon.com/appsync/latest/devguide/scalars.html#appsync-defined-scalars
